                        <interp inst="t18430130-788-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value=""></interp>NOT GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>.</p>
               <p>(There were two other indictments against the prisoner, on which Mr. Doane offered no evidence.)</p>
